div.p:
In reaching my decisions on our approach to these negotiations, I have instructed
                    the U.S. Delegation to give particular attention to three elements: (1)
                    numerical levels of the forces on both sides, taking account of throw weight;
                    (2) a program of phased mutual reductions in the level of strategic armaments;
                    and, (3) the need for qualitative as well as quantitative controls over the
                    continued competition in strategic arms.
